---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="How It Works | Links AI"
  description="What it is like to work with Links AI from first conversation through launch and ongoing improvement."
  pageClass="page-how-it-works"
>
  <section class="hero" slot="hero">
    <h1>How it works</h1>
    <p>
      This is the customer journey: what happens from the first conversation
      through delivery, launch, and ongoing improvement.
    </p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an exploratory call</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What it is like to work with us</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">01</span>
        <h3>We start with your operation</h3>
        <p>We learn how your business actually runs today, where the friction is, and which recurring workflows create the most drag.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">02</span>
        <h3>We define the right first move</h3>
        <p>We identify a practical starting point with clear scope, expected impact, and a path to implementation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">03</span>
        <h3>We build and launch with your team</h3>
        <p>We implement the solution in your real environment, test it against actual workflows, and make sure it works in practice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">04</span>
        <h3>We keep improving it</h3>
        <p>After launch, we refine the system, improve reliability, and expand the work it can handle as your needs evolve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What you should expect</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Clear communication</h3>
        <p>You should always know what we are working on, what comes next, and how the system is performing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Practical decisions</h3>
        <p>We do not force a big-bang transformation. We focus on useful systems that solve real operational problems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>A path beyond the first project</h3>
        <p>The first workflow is the start. Once it is working, we can improve it and expand into adjacent workflows.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Want to talk through your situation?</h2>
    <p>Start with an exploratory call and we will help you determine the right next step.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
